Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.99,0:01:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Phụ đề được chỉnh sửa từ phụ đề \N trên OpenSubtitles.org
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.90,0:01:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Con người đang phải\N nỗ lực để vực dậy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.63,0:01:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Từ một đợt nắng nóng\Nkỉ lục,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.67,0:01:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,và nó đang chỉ trở nên tồi tệ hơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.47,0:01:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiện giờ, nó là cơn lũ.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.40,0:01:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Toàn bộ các thị trấn đã biến\Nthành tro tàn.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.74,0:01:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Những đám cháy lúc này \Nlà tồi tệ nhất...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.34,0:01:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Nạn phá rừng đang gia tăng\N một cách nhanh chóng
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.64,0:01:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,REPORTER #4: Oxygen levels\Nplummet from deforestation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.75,0:01:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,REPORTER #5: Extinction revelers\Nlost the war today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.35,0:01:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,REPORTER #6:\N...as the last tree on Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.75,0:01:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,was logged in the Amazon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.45,0:01:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,REPORTER #7: Large areas of\Nocean algae are dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.55,0:01:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Revolution over Europe\Nnow so widespread...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.36,0:01:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,REPORTER #8: Fatal respiratory\Nillness...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.96,0:01:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,REPORTER #9: Is the biggest\Nkiller in more
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.46,0:01:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,than 100 countries\Nacross the globe.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.49,0:01:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,REPORTER #10:\NPlant life extinct,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.90,0:01:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,food rations oversubscribed...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.67,0:01:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,REPORTER #11: And supplies are\Nstretched beyond...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.37,0:01:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,REPORTER #12: What the local\Ncharities can support.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.40,0:01:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,REPORTER #13: Overpopulation in\NAfrica and the Middle East
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.64,0:01:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,now catastrophic.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.07,0:01:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,REPORTER #14: Reports of oxygen\Ncontent droptín hiệu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.77,0:02:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,REPORTER #15:\NSynthetic oxygen supplies
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.37,0:02:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,buckle under demand\Nas the UN disbands.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.31,0:02:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,REPORTER #16:\NThousands suffocate in...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.71,0:02:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,REPORTER #17: And now,\NCanada has gone dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.45,0:02:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta đã mất Ấn Độ.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.72,0:02:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,REPORTER #19: After losing\NBelgium...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.95,0:02:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Đức đã ngắt kết nối.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.38,0:02:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Trung Quốc bây giờ hoàn toàn tối đen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.99,0:02:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,REPORTER #20: In all of the\NMiddle East since January...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.59,0:02:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,REPORTER #21: O2 supplies\Ndangerously low as...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.99,0:02:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,REPORTER #22: As survivors flood\Nto the last...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.82,0:02:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,...thành phố cuối cùng \Nkhông bị bóng tối bao trùm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.68,0:02:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,GRID:\NEmergency reroute required.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.65,0:02:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,90 seconds until\Nnuclear core overload.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.57,0:03:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You down the hall tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.70,0:03:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? You going to grace us\Nwith your presence?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.08,0:03:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,JUDE: Fill up both.\NSee if she'll hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.01,0:03:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,GRID: Danger.\NEvacuate utility tunnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.78,0:03:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. She'll hold.\NAnd hell no, I'm not going.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.52,0:03:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,JUDE: Oh, come on, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.02,0:03:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,There'll be booze\Nand small talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.96,0:03:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Not for all the oxygen\Nin the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.76,0:03:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Này.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.66,0:03:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanging around a bunch\Nof lowlife foggers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.96,0:03:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Lowlife foggers\Nhave feelings too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.00,0:03:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright. Light it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.70,0:03:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.44,0:03:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,GRID: 30 seconds until overload.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.18,0:03:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Evacuation incomplete.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.14,0:03:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Utility tunnel locking down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.11,0:03:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.15,0:03:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Depressurization imminent.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.42,0:03:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you might even\Nfind yourself a wife there
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.99,0:03:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,one of these nights.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.76,0:03:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,JUDE: Another mouth to feed,\Ngreat plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.59,0:03:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,How the hell am I going to\Nhave time for a wife
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.03,0:04:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,when I'm stuck down here\Nwitín hiệu your ass every day?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.75,0:03:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,108)}10
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.75,0:03:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,108)}9
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.75,0:03:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,108)}8
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.75,0:04:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,108)}7
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.75,0:04:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,108)}6
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.75,0:04:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,108)}5
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.05,0:04:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,108)}4
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.55,0:04:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,108)}3
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.55,0:04:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,108)}2
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.55,0:04:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,108)}1
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.73,0:04:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ngay đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.93,0:04:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,ETHAN: Light it up, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.70,0:04:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.74,0:04:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,GRID: Power reroute complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.47,0:04:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,System stabilized.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.61,0:04:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Các công nhân, hãy đứng thành một hàng.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.72,0:04:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,A reminder that oxygen credits\Nare not transferable.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.69,0:04:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,ChroniCorp... Hít thở dễ dàng.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.49,0:04:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I can't, uh,\Ndo my shift tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.99,0:04:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's not a problem.\NUh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.19,0:04:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'll take it.\N- I can make it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.46,0:04:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No. It's not my fault\Nyou don't want to get paid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.53,0:04:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'll take his shift.\N- We're ahead, boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.07,0:04:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Được. Cậu vào. Anh ta ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.70,0:04:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Permanently.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.54,0:04:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hả? Không,.. này.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.77,0:04:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- ETHAN: You good?\N- JUDE: Yeah, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.11,0:04:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's more money in the pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.84,0:04:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,GRID:\NO2 is currently at 3.3%.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.55,0:04:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,ETHAN: Come on. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.58,0:04:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Where the hell is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.68,0:04:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,MAN: Hey, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.09,0:05:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,JUDE: Georgie, I need the money\Ntomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.09,0:05:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He owes me money for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.52,0:05:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Jerry.\NHow you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.49,0:05:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no fire without oxygen.\NThere's no fire without oxygen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.86,0:05:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NYou got any smart ideas?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.23,0:05:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- Get out of here.\N- There's no fire without oxygen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.63,0:05:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- Get out of here.\N- Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.17,0:05:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- Why don't you just leave it?\N- No. You listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.83,0:05:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- There's no fire without oxygen.\N- It's always something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.25,0:05:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,...for generations to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.98,0:05:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. No, listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.78,0:05:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to sacrifice it all\Nfor the generations to...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.82,0:05:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[COUGHS]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.06,0:05:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oxygen is not a privilege.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.73,0:05:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not listening,\Nand I will make you listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.73,0:05:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- Okay. Alright.\N- I need my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.63,0:05:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- Get off me.\N- My kids got the sickness too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.00,0:05:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- I will make you listen.\N- What do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.97,0:05:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- We all need to...\N- Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.07,0:05:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You know that oxygen\Nis not a privilege.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.91,0:05:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.86,0:06:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,REPORTER:\NAnother suicide protest today
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.56,0:06:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,marked the anniversary\Nof the death
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.63,0:06:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,of the last\Nliving plant in captivity.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.87,0:06:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Since the believed extinction\Nof plant life,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.30,0:06:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,deaths have continued\Nto spiral out of control
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.21,0:06:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,due to biophysical rejections\Nof the synthetic oxygen
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.98,0:06:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,that humanity\Nhas come to rely on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.15,0:06:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,As the leading distributor\Nof synthetic O2,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.98,0:06:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,ChroniCorp is still committed\Nto finding a solution
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.62,0:06:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,to this oxygen crisis that the\Nworld has termed The Sickness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.36,0:06:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,However, citizens continue\Nto revolt amid fears
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.96,0:06:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,that this may be the end\Nfor humankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.96,0:06:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,ChroniCorp's quantum physicist\NDr. Richard Whyte
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.70,0:06:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,once radically posed that\Nin the unlikely event
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.90,0:06:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,that humanity\Nsurvives this crisis,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.07,0:06:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,could we somehow find a solution
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.71,0:07:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,from our descendants\Nin the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.18,0:07:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Some suggest that his death
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.61,0:07:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,some 20 years ago\Nis linked to...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.78,0:07:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[SIGHS]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.84,0:07:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- Oh, my...\N- Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.01,0:07:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.74,0:07:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I just hear your dad's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.74,0:07:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I got something for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.41,0:07:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.71,0:07:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- Close your eyes.\N- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.18,0:07:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- Are they closed?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.99,0:07:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- Alright. Keep them closed.\N- Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.99,0:07:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep them closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.69,0:07:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.76,0:07:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Open.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.13,0:07:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you do this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.90,0:07:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,See, um, the strap is loose\Non the other one, and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I still have to seal it,\Nand, well,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.14,0:08:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,this one is compatible\Nwith the high-grade O2.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.21,0:08:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.97,0:08:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. It's fine.\NI-I-I got a new shift.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.40,0:08:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.27,0:08:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Nhưng đây là thời trang.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.11,0:08:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Nó trông tuyệt đẹp.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.31,0:08:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Đương nhiên.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.44,0:08:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Thật luôn?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.01,0:08:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ồ, sao vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.75,0:08:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Anh không muốn trở nên\N lung linh sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.08,0:08:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Em định làm gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.40,0:08:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Đâu có
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.75,0:08:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't... Don't start this again.\NRemember what they said.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.89,0:08:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- You need to calm down.\N- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.25,0:08:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You need... you... you...\Nyou need to relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.10,0:08:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Thôi chết.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.33,0:08:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Em không sao chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.49,0:09:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Xin lỗi anh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.20,0:09:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Cứ việc để đó cho anh
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.17,0:09:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Không sao đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.93,0:09:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Làm ơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.71,0:09:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Nó ổn mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.14,0:09:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Chết tiệt.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.92,0:09:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.82,0:09:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.86,0:09:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Công dân số 34465?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.43,0:09:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.23,0:09:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been instructed\Nto bring you upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.07,0:09:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,JUDE: We've got clearance\Nto be down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.00,0:09:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't like to be touched.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.97,0:09:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Anh ta đi nếu tôi đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.81,0:09:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Chỉ việc xem họ muốn nói gì thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.28,0:09:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Đi nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.98,0:09:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoan nghênh công dân.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.78,0:09:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the Applied Sciences\NDivision of ChroniCorp.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.12,0:10:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,ChroniCorp is proud to be\Nthe largest supplier
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.29,0:10:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,of breathable air\Nto the people of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.96,0:10:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,ChroniCorp... Breathe easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.80,0:10:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoan nghênh công dân.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.43,0:10:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the Applied Sciences\NDivision of ChroniCorp.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.97,0:10:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,ChroniCorp is proud to be\Nthe largest supplier
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.14,0:10:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,of breathable air\Nto the people of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.12,0:10:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,REGINA: Even the fires\Nburn themselves out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.16,0:10:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Họ cũng không thể hít thở được.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.90,0:10:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Tên tôi là Regina Jackson.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.60,0:10:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the CTO of\NParticle Research.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.34,0:10:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Còn cậu là... Ethan Whyte.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.11,0:10:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ừm, đúng, là tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.05,0:11:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Vợ cậu thế nào?\NOur records show...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.05,0:11:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Tôi đang chăm sóc cho cô ấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.62,0:11:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We've all accepted\Nthat things today
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.92,0:11:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,are even worse\Nthan what scientists predicted.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.50,0:11:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact is\Nthe O2 rejection epidemic
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.20,0:11:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,is going to wipe out the human\Nrace within a handful of years.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.17,0:11:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate you bringing us\Nup here, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.90,0:11:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,but what exactly\Nare you offering?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.34,0:11:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Sẽ ra sao nếu tôi nói rằng\N cậu có thể cứu lấy chúng ta?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.61,0:11:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'd hate to seem like\NI don't appreciate
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.58,0:11:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,this show-and-tell,\Nbut I think we should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.12,0:11:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,REGINA: Your security\Nhas been upgraded.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.55,0:11:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Cậu sẽ được thông báo tại phòng thí nghiệm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.17,0:11:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to our Hail Mary.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.23,0:11:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Meet the Chronicle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.20,0:12:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.34,0:12:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Billy Mitchell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.21,0:12:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,An absolute honor\Nto meet you, Ethan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.92,0:12:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.52,0:12:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thật thú vị.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.99,0:12:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ethan, do you know\Nwhat your father did here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.94,0:12:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Được rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.31,0:12:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,3 phút, 10 giây.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.08,0:12:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Calibration is within tolerance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.28,0:12:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,REGINA: It's taken us 20 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.35,0:12:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If only your father\Ncould see this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.99,0:12:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,My father's not here, is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.43,0:12:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Of course. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.23,0:12:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,During our first trial,\Nwe tested the Chronicle
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.47,0:13:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,with something that wouldn't\Ntake as much power as matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.44,0:13:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,radio waves to act\Nlike a sort of tín hiệu
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.17,0:13:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,to see what was\Non the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.17,0:13:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The radio waves bounced back,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.41,0:13:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,but they had been changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.11,0:13:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Có thứ gì đó được mã hóa bên trong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.21,0:13:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Bounced back, what?\NWhat do you mean, bounced back?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.12,0:13:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,From where?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.42,0:13:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Not where, when.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.09,0:13:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Chúng tôi đã nhận được một tin nhấn từ tương lai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.26,0:13:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Từ tương lai?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.43,0:13:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a fucking time machine?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.43,0:13:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Cách hiện tại 407 năm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.67,0:13:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,400 năm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.03,0:13:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Bà đang nói với tôi rằng \Nloài người vẫn còn sống?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.07,0:13:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Tin nhắn này ngắn gọn, Ethan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.64,0:13:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Grid, giải mã\Ntệp tin Chronicle số 170681.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.08,0:13:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Trên kia.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.55,0:13:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,GỬI............................
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.30,0:13:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,GỬI ETHAN..............
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.38,0:14:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,GỬI ETHAN WHITE
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.70,0:14:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,REGINA: The people\Nwho sent the message
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.37,0:14:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,must have found a cure\Nfor the O2 sickness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.14,0:14:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Nó là điều không thể.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.64,0:14:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no other way\Nthey could still be alive
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.41,0:14:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,that far in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.74,0:14:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We think they want to give\Nthe cure to us
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.38,0:14:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,so that we could\Nsave more people here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.05,0:14:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Why ask for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.72,0:14:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't exactly know why,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.69,0:14:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,but we may only get one shot\Nat sending someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.76,0:14:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,One shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.63,0:14:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The Chronicle feeds off the\Nnuclear reactor under the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.56,0:14:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Just to fire a clock\Na few phút through time
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.50,0:14:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,knocks large sections\Nof the city off the grid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.27,0:14:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,To fire the mass\Nof a human that far?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.80,0:14:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just say I hope we\Ndon't have to try this twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.37,0:14:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do I get the feeling\Nthat there's a catch?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.41,0:14:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ethan, we don't know yet\Nhow to bring you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.72,0:15:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to shoot me\Ninto oblivion with...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.62,0:15:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,with no way to get home?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.29,0:15:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Cậu phải tìm ra\Nnhững người đã gửi tin nhắn này.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.33,0:15:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Họ có thể giúp cậu quay trở về.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.60,0:15:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You have got to find the cure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.77,0:15:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You may be humanity's\Nonly chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.87,0:15:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You may be your wife's\Nonly chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.48,0:15:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,MAN: Beautiful, crisp,\Nclean air, all you can breathe,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.18,0:15:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,chỉ 20$/h.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.72,0:15:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,JUDE: Have you ever seen\Nanything like that shit before?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.76,0:15:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- Two more.\N- It's all very impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.33,0:15:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not leaving Xanthe\Nas a favor to those ghouls.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.60,0:15:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.54,0:15:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He's buying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.44,0:15:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[SPEAKS INDISTINCTLY]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.88,0:16:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,À. Được rồi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.55,0:16:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Có vấn đề gì với em vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.69,0:16:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Gì cơ?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.63,0:16:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Anh... anh có thực sự tin rằng\Nem sẽ đi cứu thế giới?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.53,0:16:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Very romantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.80,0:16:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to take this seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.30,0:16:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Your old man believed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.60,0:16:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,My old man was a fool\Nand a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.44,0:16:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What if there's more\Nto his story, Ethan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.92,0:16:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Story?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.35,0:16:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to hear more?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.79,0:16:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,A father leaves a suicide note\Nfor his 8-year-old son.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.19,0:16:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If he'd just been there instead\Nof chasing fucking rainbows,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.33,0:16:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,my mother would\Nstill be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.64,0:16:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Very heroic,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.37,0:16:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and as if this wasn't enough\Nof a reminder of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.64,0:17:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,you want me to do what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.41,0:17:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow in his footsteps\Nto leave my sick wife to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.96,0:17:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember when I brought you\Ndown in the tunnels
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.92,0:17:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.83,0:17:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You were so scared\Nof just being left alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.83,0:17:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Còn nhớ những gì anh nói không?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.90,0:17:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,"Without the darkness,\Nthere's no light."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.34,0:17:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.81,0:17:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Má em.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.34,0:17:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Nghe này, cái đầu ngốc.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.38,0:17:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been through hell\Nand back in this life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.88,0:17:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I've lost my family,\Ndamn near lost my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.52,0:17:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been working in\Nthose fucking tunnels
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.89,0:17:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,for as long as I can remember,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.32,0:17:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and the only thing\NI know that works
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.66,0:17:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,is when we fight for ourselves,\Nprotect what's ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.39,0:17:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I can protect Xanthe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.29,0:17:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not just going\Nto abandon her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.30,0:18:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And what are you going to do\Nwhen she gets worse?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This ain't about\Nsaving the world, bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.28,0:18:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Em muốn chứng minh\Nrằng em không như ông ta?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.02,0:18:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Cứu cô ấy đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.82,0:18:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOOR OPENS]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.39,0:19:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been waiting for you\Nall day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.98,0:19:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,RICHARD: I made this for you,\NEthy,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.54,0:19:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,because I have it\Non good authority
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.91,0:19:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,that you are going to grow up\Nto be someone very important.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.48,0:19:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,A science man?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.09,0:19:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,A science man.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.73,0:19:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, this is going to hurt\Na little,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.06,0:19:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,but it will help you become\Nwho you are meant to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.57,0:19:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, one day you'll understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.41,0:19:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You will want to trust what you\Ncan see with your own eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.14,0:19:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,but it won't be enough, and you\Nwill need to make a choice
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.38,0:19:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,about whether you believe\Nin something bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.12,0:20:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Believe in what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.03,0:20:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Believe in people.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.68,0:20:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[WHIRS]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.98,0:20:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[GASPS]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.01,0:20:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[BREATHING SHAKILY]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.46,0:20:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Ethy.\NYou're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.59,0:20:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't come off.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.63,0:20:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,SELENE: What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.43,0:20:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,ETHAN: Papa...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.20,0:20:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,SELENE: Don't you dare\Nleave us again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.68,0:21:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,When?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.52,0:21:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not leaving you to chase\Nsome stupid fantasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.76,0:21:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You think a second chance\Nis a fantasy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.79,0:21:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.53,0:21:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Fucking scientists.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.03,0:21:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think your tool kit\Nis important right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.97,0:21:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,My tools need to be clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.64,0:21:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.67,0:21:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I have responsibilities here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.84,0:21:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to meet my shifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.07,0:21:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We're... We're so close
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.57,0:21:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,to having enough for\Nthe high-grade O2.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.14,0:21:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That could help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.65,0:21:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It could slow down the symptoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.85,0:21:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do that.\NDon't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.08,0:21:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.69,0:21:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You can say that you're afraid,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.12,0:21:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,but don't you dare use me\Nas an excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.92,0:21:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You're better than that, Ethan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.56,0:21:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.56,0:21:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.56,0:21:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You're everything to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.90,0:21:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I can look after you.\NI can help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.94,0:21:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I can make more money.\NI can make you okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.81,0:21:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's to say that time\Nis anything
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.61,0:22:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,we should mess with anyway?\NWhat if I can't change anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.61,0:22:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's to say that we can't?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.94,0:22:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. What if I could?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.55,0:22:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What if I mess with something,\Nand it makes everything worse?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.59,0:22:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe what I'm hearing\Nright now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.96,0:22:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I'm not going to risk\Nlosing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.99,0:22:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,XANTHE: You can't lose me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.63,0:22:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.56,0:22:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to have faith, Eth,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.80,0:22:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,that you can be bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.11,0:22:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Faith isn't going\Nto protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.58,0:22:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Now is not the time to have\Nyour tail between your legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.65,0:22:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We're a team.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.05,0:22:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Why aren't you on my side?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.76,0:22:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Last year, I had\N20 kids in my class.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.06,0:22:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This year, I have 12.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.16,0:22:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw three of them suffocate\Nright in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.07,0:23:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the only one\NI care about.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.94,0:23:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be with you\Nif I thought that was true.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.15,0:23:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid too, Ethan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.09,0:23:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that you'll come back\Nto me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.36,0:23:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Em tin vào anh.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.33,0:24:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Cha!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.30,0:24:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Khốn khiếp.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.77,0:24:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Cha...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.14,0:24:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.41,0:24:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Cha em không còn đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.78,0:24:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[BREATHING HEAVILY]
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.89,0:24:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[SCREAMS]
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.09,0:25:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care if I can only find\None dose of this cure.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.13,0:25:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Xanthe gets the first one,\Nor I'm not going.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.17,0:25:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You need me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.50,0:25:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Được, Ethan.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.50,0:25:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Chúng ta có thỏa thuận.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.23,0:25:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,ETHAN WHYTE \N DỰ ÁN CHRONICAL SỐ 14
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.38,0:25:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,BILLY: These aren't just\Nspace suits, Ethan.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.38,0:26:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,These are my babies.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.81,0:26:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Fenrir is not quite ready,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.22,0:26:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,but, Tyr, she'll get you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.45,0:26:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.09,0:26:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The Chronicle, at this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.39,0:26:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,can't tether to itself\Nin the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.39,0:26:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something wrong\Nat the other end.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.36,0:26:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.96,0:26:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It means we're going to\Nhave to throw you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.27,0:26:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ném tôi ra đó?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.87,0:26:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,BILLY: Without being tethered\Nat the other end,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.07,0:26:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,there's a chance you could land
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.91,0:26:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,inside a mountain\Nor the ocean, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.01,0:26:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to be kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.18,0:26:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to aim a little higher.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.21,0:26:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[BREATHING HEAVILY]
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.88,0:26:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,REGINA: We'll land you as close\Nas we can
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.19,0:26:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,to the source\Nof the radio waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.16,0:26:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You just find the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.96,0:26:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Track them down and bring\Nthe cure back home to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.39,0:26:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,ETHAN: Sounds easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.53,0:26:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This may be humankind's\Nmost critical journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.27,0:26:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you to find\Na way back, Ethan.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.11,0:27:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Được rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.95,0:27:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Một lần nữa, tập trung.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.58,0:27:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Đây là ai?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.32,0:27:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Archie.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.45,0:27:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Đúng rồi
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.92,0:27:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Archie có thể làm gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.49,0:27:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,ETHAN: Um, systems analysis,\Nnavigation, communication.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.06,0:27:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ừ. Đúng rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.16,0:27:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Archie là người bạn duy nhất của cậu,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.06,0:27:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,nên bảo quản cô ấy thật tốt.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.93,0:27:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The suit will feed your vitals\Nback to us from Archie,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.20,0:27:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,so we're going\Nto know you're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.10,0:27:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.57,0:27:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hít thở sâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.47,0:27:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Nhìn chú này.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.58,0:27:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Đừng để mất.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.88,0:27:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Định thời lượng tử chuyển tiếp.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.20,0:27:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Chăm sóc cô ấy giùm em.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.17,0:27:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Cho tới khi em quay về thôi đấy.
