Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.10,0:43:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thế này đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.51,0:43:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Con thấy đấy, Ethy,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.44,0:43:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta sẽ không để \N chuyện gì xảy đến với con.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.55,0:43:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.59,0:43:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.00,0:44:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.20,0:44:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Khốn khiếp!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.01,0:44:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Đồ khỉ gió!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.26,0:44:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.95,0:44:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,A!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.16,0:45:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.27,0:45:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.67,0:45:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Chờ đã, Ethan.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.44,0:45:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ngươi không phải thật!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.07,0:45:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ngươi không phải thật!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.21,0:45:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ethan, em đang ảo giác.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.04,0:45:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Cái... Cái gì cơ?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.31,0:45:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Em tự đầu đọc chính mình...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.48,0:45:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,bằng quả việt quất.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.19,0:45:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.27,0:45:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Jude?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.40,0:45:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sẽ ổn thôi, nhóc. Miễn là làm theo\N những gì anh nói.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.04,0:45:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ngay sau đó, bọn anh biết \Ncó gì đó không ổn.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.41,0:46:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Bên anh nghe thấy \Nmạch đập của em vọng lại.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.65,0:46:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Rồi độc tính trong máu tăng đột biến.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.72,0:46:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Chất độc.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.72,0:46:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Tim ngừng đập.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.16,0:46:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Biết không, anh \Nchứng kiến em chết đấy, Eth.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.73,0:46:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Em đâu có chết.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.47,0:46:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,đúng không?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.44,0:46:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Anh không nghĩ vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.61,0:46:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Nhưng Billy nói rằng chú ấy\Nchỉ có đủ năng lượng...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.21,0:46:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,để kích hoạt Chronicle lần cuối.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.28,0:46:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Anh chộp lấy bộ đồ thứ 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.15,0:46:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Không thể bỏ em lại đây một mình.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.02,0:46:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Anh nói với chú rằng\N anh có thể đưa em về.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.03,0:46:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Anh đến vì em.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.63,0:46:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Anh rơi xuống đất như tấn gạch.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.33,0:46:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mọi thứ bị thiêu rụi...\Ncả bộ đồ của anh nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.04,0:47:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Chỉ là anh mừng vì nhóc còn sống,\Nhạnh phúc khi thấy cái đầu ngốc của em,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.11,0:47:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,hạnh phúc vì có thể thở\N mà không cần cái mặt nạ chết tiệt đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.21,0:47:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Xanthe?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.32,0:47:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Cô ấy thực sự cần em.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.19,0:47:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Có vấn đề ở đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.93,0:47:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Cái quái gì đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.13,0:47:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Em đã nghĩ anh cứu em,\Nnhưng em vẫn chết.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.26,0:47:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,ETHAN WHYTE \N DỰ ÁN CHRONICAL SỐ 14
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.20,0:47:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Không đúng.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.77,0:47:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Không. Cái này không đúng.\NÝ anh là, đây không phải em.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.38,0:47:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Anh vừa nói là\Nem bị đầu đọc mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.71,0:47:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Đã từng.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.52,0:47:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ý anh, bọn anh đã thay đổi điều đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.49,0:47:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,đúng không nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.10,0:47:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Có gì đó rất bất ổn.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.40,0:47:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Anh nghĩ gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.77,0:48:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Nghe này, ở đây còn gì nữa không?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.10,0:48:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Là... Là cái gì cơ?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.21,0:48:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Một cây súng à?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.58,0:48:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Em nghĩ ai đó để lại cái lỗ\N đó trên đầu em rồi bỏ trốn.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.52,0:48:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Nghe này, cái chỗ xương chết tiệt \Nnày không phải em.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.49,0:48:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Lại ăn quả mọng rồi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.70,0:48:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Xem nào, ai đó đã gửi cho em,\Ncái để họ sống sót
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.10,0:48:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,mất khoảng lâu để tái tạo nơi này,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.31,0:48:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hẳn họ đã tìm ra phương pháp.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.24,0:48:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Nếu em không tìm họ lúc này,\NXanthe...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.15,0:48:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Rồi, tìm họ thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.15,0:48:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ử
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.28,0:48:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Có lí do để chúng ta tới đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.13,0:48:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Giờ ta sẽ đi theo hướng đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.84,0:49:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Bão hòa đèn hiệu khẩn cấp đạt 98%.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.37,0:49:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Gần hơn rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.72,0:49:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Sẵn sàng chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.73,0:49:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Xem có ai ở nhà không.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.76,0:49:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Anh trông vào em.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.80,0:50:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.23,0:50:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Xin chào?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.80,0:50:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Cẩn thận.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.57,0:50:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Xin chào?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.21,0:50:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ethan!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.38,0:50:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Này, ở lại đi, Jude.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.96,0:51:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Chẳng thấy gì cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.02,0:51:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,CHÀO ETHAN WHYTE
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.63,0:51:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,NHẤN ENTER ĐỂ KÍCH HOẠT
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.07,0:52:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Kích hoạt gì cơ?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.46,0:52:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,KHỞI TẠO MẪU DNA
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.33,0:52:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,A!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.36,0:52:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Chết tiệt!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.97,0:52:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ra ngoài ngay!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.03,0:52:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,ĐÃ CẤP QUYỀN TRUY CẬP: ETHAN WHYTE
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.90,0:52:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,ĐÃ PHÂN TÍCH MẪU DNA
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.11,0:52:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Truy cập?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.77,0:53:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Không thể nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.77,0:53:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Chào bạn, Grid 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.50,0:53:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Là Hail Mary đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.60,0:53:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Xin chào, hạ cấp xuống 1270.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.78,0:53:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ethan Whyte, đã xác thực danh tính DNA.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.88,0:53:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Đã cấp quyền truy cập Chronicle.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.82,0:53:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Bắt đầu trình tự chuẩn bị cổng thông tin.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.68,0:53:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Bắt đầu đếm ngược.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.09,0:53:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Cổng sẽ kích hoạt trong bốn giờ.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.09,0:53:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thời điểm: năm 2067 SCN.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.66,0:53:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ethan.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.10,0:53:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ethan, nếu những thứ này \Nvẫn còn hoạt động,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.70,0:53:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,chúng ta có thể dùng nó để về nhà.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.97,0:53:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Mọi người đâu cả rồi?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.97,0:53:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Trông chẳng giống nhà của ai cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.64,0:53:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Điều này thật vô lí.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.15,0:53:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai hết cả rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.75,0:53:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Anh chỉ đang nhìn thấy những gì trước mắt,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.02,0:53:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,rồi thấy một cái thuyền cứu sinh.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.62,0:53:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Em tưởng anh đã cứu em\Nkhỏi chất độc
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.42,0:53:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Rằng nó đã thay đổi cả quá trình
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.59,0:53:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Rõ ràng, chẳng có gì thay đổi cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.86,0:54:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Nghĩa là sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.63,0:54:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Nghĩa là có thứ gì đó \Ncòn lớn hơn đang diễn ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.20,0:54:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Lúc mà thiết bị này quét máu của em,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.17,0:54:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Cái đèn, vừa nãy nó mới màu đỏ.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.87,0:54:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,giờ nó thành màu xanh rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.14,0:54:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Cái này, của bộ xương đấy,\Ncũng là màu xanh.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.71,0:54:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Rồi sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.21,0:54:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Nghĩa là em đã từng chết ở đây rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.65,0:54:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Mỗi bước em đi, anh ta cũng thế
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.65,0:54:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Em chết hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.45,0:54:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Em có đang lắng nghe\N bản thân không đấy?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.48,0:54:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Làm thế nào nó xảy ra được?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.02,0:54:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Anh ta giống như tương lai của em.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.20,0:54:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Như kiểu em trở thành anh ta vậy
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.69,0:54:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Đó là điều không thể!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.16,0:54:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Em cần phải hạ mình xuống.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.53,0:54:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Em đang mất trí đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.79,0:54:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Grid?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.78,0:54:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Vâng, Ethan?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.74,0:54:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Thứ này có cho tôi quyền truy cập\N vào dữ liệu sao lưu của Chronicle không?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.01,0:54:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Vâng, Ethan.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.64,0:54:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Giải mã nhật kí hệ thống.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.95,0:54:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Nhật kí Chronicle số 1...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.95,0:54:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Chúng ta đang ở khởi đầu của hành trình
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.99,0:55:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,có thể thay đổi mọi thứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.99,0:55:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Tôi là\NGiáo sư Richard Whyte,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.83,0:55:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,nhà vật lí đứng đầu dự án Chronicle.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.86,0:55:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Chúng tôi đã phát hiện ra \Nsự bất thường trong trường Higgs,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.70,0:55:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,điều có thể sớm cho phép gửi sóng vô tuyến
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.00,0:55:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,và cả vật chất theo thời gian.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.67,0:55:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Dừng!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.18,0:55:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Em nghĩ gì khi nghĩ rằng có thể tìm ra
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.68,0:55:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,thứ em đang tìm kiếm?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.15,0:55:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Em phải làm.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.52,0:55:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Không, đừng làm thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.79,0:55:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Chúng tôi đã lấp một \Ntrạm giám sát khí quyển.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.86,0:55:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Nó sẽ tiếp tục hoạt động,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.22,0:55:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,và cho đến khi đạt đến \Nthời điểm ở tương lai
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.86,0:55:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,khi không khí có thể thở được,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.66,0:55:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,nó sẽ gửi dữ liệu cho chúng tôi qua Chronicle.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.97,0:55:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hy vọng của chúng tôi là Chronicle\Nsẽ giúp ta học được
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.83,0:55:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,từ con cháu ta cách họ\Nbổ sung oxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.57,0:55:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Đủ rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.27,0:55:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Cái này hại nhiều hơn giúp.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.84,0:55:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Em đâu thể trốn khỏi ông ấy mãi được.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.81,0:55:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Làm ơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.32,0:56:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Nhật kí số 97.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.02,0:56:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Cố gắng lên nào mọi người.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.26,0:56:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Chuẩn bị đếm ngược.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.44,0:56:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Toàn bộ cuộc sống của chúng ta\N dồn vào khoảnh khắc này.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.67,0:56:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Chúng tôi đang chuẩn bị cho\Nđối tượng Chronicle thứ nhất,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.91,0:56:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Gói sóng vô tuyến sẽ gửi tới
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.75,0:56:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Chronicle ở tương lai.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.61,0:56:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Nếu thành công,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.12,0:56:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Chúng tôi sẽ nhận được tiếng vang\N của dữ liệu về mức độ oxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.02,0:56:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Gửi tín hiệu trong
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.10,0:56:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Gửi tín hiệu trong 3
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.00,0:56:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Gửi tín hiệu trong 2
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.91,0:56:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Gửi tín hiệu trong 1
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.00,0:56:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Đã nhận tiếng vang.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.30,0:56:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Tín hiệu trở lại.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.84,0:56:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thời gian... năm 2474 SCN.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.28,0:57:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoạt động rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.88,0:57:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Dữ liệu đã được giải mã.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.08,0:57:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Dữ liệu đã được ghi đè thủ công tại đầu cuối.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.72,0:57:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Các từ tiếng Anh đã được giải mã\N trong bộ phiên dịch.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.00,0:57:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,GỬI............................
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.40,0:57:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,GỬI ETHAN..............
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.27,0:57:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,GỬI ETHAN WHITE
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.02,0:57:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Tiếng Anh? Gì cơ?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.67,0:57:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Chúa ơi.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.42,0:57:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Nó nói cái gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.92,0:57:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Tôi đâu có làm chuyện này.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.36,0:57:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Sao có thể xảy ra được?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.23,0:57:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ông cần phải thực hiện thành công thứ này.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.36,0:57:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Nó đang hoạt động.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.26,0:57:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Có ai đang nhắc đến con trai tôi..
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.97,0:58:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thế quái nào họ biết được con trai ông?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.04,0:58:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Tôi không biết được.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.44,0:58:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Đừng nói với tôi như vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.91,0:58:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Tất cả chúng ta là một gia đình.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.81,0:58:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Nó đang hoạt động.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.81,0:58:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ai đó đã gửi cho ta tin nhắn này.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.05,0:58:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Bên đầu kia có ai đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.25,0:58:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Vậy thì ta chuyển sang giai đoạn kế tiếp
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.05,0:58:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Bao lâu nữa chúng ta \Ncó thể thử nghiệm việc gửi vật chất?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.29,0:58:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Không thể.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.72,0:58:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Nói.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.99,0:58:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Có một vấn đề với năng lượng ở năm 2474.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.13,0:58:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Cảnh báo
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.00,0:58:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Lõi năng lượng hạt nhân ngừng hoạt động
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.27,0:58:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Cảnh báo
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.19,0:58:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hệ thống Chronicle ngừng hoạt động
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.04,0:58:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Archie, chẩn đoán.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.80,0:58:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Lõi hạt nhân,\Nnguồn điện lạnh tổng hợp gặp trục trặc.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.24,0:58:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Nghĩa là sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.57,0:58:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Cổng sẽ không liên kết tới năm 2067, Ethan.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.38,0:58:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Không đủ năng lượng.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.01,0:58:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Archie, tìm nơi phát sinh lỗi?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.62,0:58:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Đang tìm....
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.89,0:58:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Phòng điều khiển lõi năng lượng,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.49,0:58:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Truy cập đường hầm dịch vụ số 7.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.86,0:58:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Grid?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.72,0:58:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Vâng, Jude Mathers?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.23,0:59:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Tại sao việc đếm ngược\N không dừng lại được?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.06,0:59:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Jude Mathers,\Ntrình tự thiết lập của Chronicle
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.06,0:59:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,đã thực hiện và không thể dừng lại được.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.33,0:59:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hệ thống sẽ đạt đến \Nmức độ hạt không ổn định.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.74,0:59:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Không ổn định là sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.10,0:59:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Nếu nguồn cấp điện không được nối lại
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.04,0:59:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,trước khi đếm ngược trở về 0,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.31,0:59:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Các hạt tích điện trong Chronicle
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.41,0:59:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,sẽ tạo ra một vụ nổ hạt nhân.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.78,0:59:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Vụ nổ hạt nhân nghe không ổn chút nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.18,0:59:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Đừng chết lúc này, Eth.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.29,0:59:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Khoan đã.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.45,0:59:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Nếu họ đã nhận được tin nhắn này từ trước,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.69,0:59:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,hẳn họ đã biết về lỗi năng lượng.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.39,0:59:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Grid, nếu ta sửa được\Nnguồn của Chronicle,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.06,0:59:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Cổng sẽ mở trong bao lâu\N trước khi lõi hạt nhân cạn kiệt?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.13,0:59:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Một khi đếm ngược trở về 0,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.37,0:59:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Cổng sẽ kết nối đến năm 2067\N trong khoảng 30 giây.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.38,0:59:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,JUDE: Eth, mất một lúc ta\N mới có thể xuống tới lõi được.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.44,0:59:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Chúng ta cần thực hiện ngay giờ.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.42,0:59:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thưa chúa Jesus
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.82,0:59:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Người có thấy những gì\N con vừa thấy không?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.92,1:00:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Có ai đó gửi tín hiệu từ đây!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.36,1:00:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,C-có nghĩa là\Nhọ đã sửa nơi này.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.93,1:00:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Nghĩa là họ hẳn phải có phương pháp!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.39,1:00:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Họ có thể giúp em cứu lấy Xanthe.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.03,1:00:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ừ thì, ai đó đã gửi tin nhắn,\Nhọ đâu có ở đây.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.43,1:00:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sao họ lại không nói cho ta biết\Nvề lỗi năng lượng?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.47,1:00:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sao họ lại cử anh đến?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.41,1:00:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hả?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.84,1:00:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Anh đến để cứu em mà,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.24,1:00:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,tiêm thuốc giải vào \Ncơ thể đã chết của em.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.41,1:00:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Nhưng sao lại không gửi một người lính...\Nhay là một bác sĩ?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.32,1:00:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ừ thì, còn ai đó suýt nữa tự sát
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.82,1:00:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,để cứu lấy cái mông \Nvô ơn của em nữa đây?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.16,1:00:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Nghe này.\NEm đã đúng.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.56,1:00:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta không thể cứu lấy mọi người,\Nnhưng anh có thể cứu lấy em.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.00,1:00:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Đi thôi.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.00,1:00:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Khoan
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.53,1:00:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Em đang nhầm lẫn.\NEm cần tìm ra điều này.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.23,1:00:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Chúng ta chỉ có một lần \Nđể sửa thứ này thôi
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.30,1:00:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Một lần thôi đấy, Ethan.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.24,1:00:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Anh không thể làm mà thiếu em được,\Nnên cùng kiểm soát đi.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.21,1:01:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Chúng ta cần kiểm soát,\Nem trai à.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.15,1:01:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Em cần... cần chút thời gian.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.02,1:01:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Vậy em không muốn gặp lại\NXanthe lần nữa sao?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.12,1:01:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ai cho anh nói thế với cô ấy.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.49,1:01:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Anh đang không định để em\Ntự giết chính mình đâu đấy.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.52,1:01:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Bỏ em ra.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.43,1:01:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Làm ơn, tỉnh lại đi, nhóc.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.00,1:01:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ý anh, anh chưa bao giờ để em thất vọng,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.81,1:01:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,nên đừng để anh thất vọng lúc này.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.21,1:01:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Vụ nổ hạt nhân sẽ xảy ra \Ntrong 3 giờ 50 phút nữa.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.35,1:01:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Được rồi.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.95,1:01:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Có ai đó đã gửi tin nhắn, \Nhọ không có ở đây.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.59,1:01:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Bây giờ ta chỉ cần đi xuống \Nđường hầm dẫn vào.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.16,1:01:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta chỉ cần bật nguồn lên,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.56,1:01:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,rồi sau đó sẽ có đủ\N thời gian để tìm ra họ.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.40,1:01:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,3 giờ, 50 phút,\Ntích tắc.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.61,1:02:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thành phố lẽ ra phải ở ngay đây.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.56,1:02:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,KHU VỰC CÂY OXY
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.58,1:04:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Họ không bao giờ tìm ra\N cách để tồn tại cả.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.15,1:04:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Trái Đất chỉ việc chờ\N chúng ta chết mà thôi.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.53,1:05:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Eth, em đưa chúng ta tới đâu thế?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.80,1:05:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Đây không phải là cách đâu.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.58,1:05:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,BÀ XANTHE WHYTE - LỊCH SỬ VỀ THỰC VẬT
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.36,1:06:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Họ chỉ vừa mới chết\Nngay trong lớp học,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.16,1:06:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,chỉ vừa mới ngồi đây.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.77,1:06:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Mọi thứ giờ trở nên tệ hơn.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.77,1:06:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Họ thậm chí còn không loại bỏ người chết.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.88,1:06:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Nghĩa là ta đã thất bại rồi sao?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.62,1:06:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Eth.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.52,1:06:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Eth.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.26,1:06:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Đừng, Eth.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.63,1:06:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ethan.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.78,1:07:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Xanthe.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.22,1:07:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Không sao đâu em.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.00,1:07:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,ANH SẼ TÌM RA CON ĐƯỜNG TRỞ VỀ
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.44,1:07:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,ƯỚC GÌ ANH QUAY TRỞ LẠI
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.24,1:07:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sao anh dám đi như vậy hả.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.28,1:07:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Anh đâu rồi, Richard?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.65,1:07:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Anh vừa làm gì con vậy?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.42,1:07:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Không. Hả? Không.\NEm... không...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.96,1:07:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Không, em không hiểu.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.39,1:07:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Anh cần phải tự nói với con mình đi.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.93,1:07:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ethy...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.33,1:07:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ethy, nghe ta nói đây.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.96,1:07:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta cần con đi bộ với mẹ một chút.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.43,1:08:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Con muốn ở nhà.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.46,1:08:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta sẽ gặp con
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.31,1:08:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta hứa.\NCon hiểu không?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.54,1:08:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Con phải tin bố lúc này.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.89,1:08:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Được rồi con.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.32,1:08:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Trèo qua đó đi con.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.99,1:08:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Nhanh, trèo đi con, chỉ cần làm thôi.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.56,1:08:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Cứ đi đi con.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.83,1:08:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Mẹ!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.73,1:08:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Trèo đi
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.96,1:08:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Cứ leo lên đi.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.57,1:08:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Mẹ!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:33.29,1:08:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ethan
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.50,1:08:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Chúng tôi không có tiền.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.81,1:08:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Làm ơn, nó chỉ là một đứa bé thôi.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.51,1:08:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Làm ơn. Đừng!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.58,1:08:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Không!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.79,1:08:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Không!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.34,1:08:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Mẹ ơi.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.76,1:09:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Đừng.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.70,1:09:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Mẹ ơi, đừng mà.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.71,1:09:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Mẹ ơi.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.88,1:09:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Mẹ sẽ mãi bên con.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.78,1:09:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Không!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.95,1:09:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Mẹ ơi!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.75,1:09:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ba ơi.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.86,1:10:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ba ơi.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.86,1:10:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ba ơi.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.96,1:10:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ba ơi.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.51,1:10:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ba ơi.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.06,1:10:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hít thở đi.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.96,1:10:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Gắng lên, thở đi.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.53,1:10:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Em cần phải đấu tranh\Ncho bản thân mình lúc này.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.70,1:10:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ba em không còn đây nữa.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.04,1:10:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thở đi.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.84,1:10:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thở đi.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:57.11,1:11:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- Không!\N- Thở đi.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.09,1:11:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Thở đi.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.02,1:11:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thở đi.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.19,1:11:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Em đây rồi.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.93,1:11:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- Chúa ơi.\N- Em vừa trở lại với cô ấy.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.23,1:11:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Em phải...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.67,1:11:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Anh biết.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.67,1:11:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sao em lại có thể bỏ cô ấy một mình?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.07,1:11:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Được rồi, em đã làm những \Ngì em cho là đúng, Eth.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.68,1:11:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Có đúng không?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.49,1:11:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Em đã hứa với cô ấy sẽ trở lại mà.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.80,1:11:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Chúng ta kiểm soát số phận\N của mình đúng không?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.10,1:11:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Chỉ cần có mấy cái niềm tin chết tiệt.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.44,1:12:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Chỉ cần có niềm tin.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.01,1:12:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,E-Em không thể\N để mất cô ấy thêm nữa.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.22,1:12:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Đây không phải lỗi của em.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.65,1:12:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Em bỏ mặc cô ấy chết.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.84,1:12:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Này.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:17.29,1:12:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Em không phải ông ta, Eth.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.11,1:12:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Nếu ta không thể \Nthay đổi mọi thứ thì sao?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.81,1:12:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Có lẽ đây không phải nơi của chúng ta.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.28,1:12:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Không thể nào.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.32,1:12:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hẳn phải có cách nào đó...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.37,1:12:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Chỉ toàn bụi và... bụi và xương.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.18,1:12:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Không thể là lối đi duy nhất được.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.16,1:12:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Không thể.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.39,1:12:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ta...\N- Đừng lòng vòng nữa.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.47,1:12:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Có lẽ thế này sẽ tốt hơn.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.00,1:13:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sẽ không ai bị ảnh hưởng nữa.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.04,1:13:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Đi nào.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.02,1:13:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Anh vừa nói gì?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.21,1:13:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hả?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.98,1:13:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Gì?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.62,1:13:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Archie...\NArchie, phát lại đoạn ghi cuối.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.92,1:13:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ai đấy?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.99,1:13:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Có lẽ thế này sẽ tốt hơn.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.06,1:13:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Sẽ không ai bị ảnh hưởng nữa.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:28.02,1:13:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Xung đột dữ liệu.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.00,1:13:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Bỏ qua đoạn đầu.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.30,1:13:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Em phải hy sinh những gì?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.10,1:13:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Anh làm chuyện này vì em.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.00,1:13:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Anh làm chỉ vì bản thân mình thôi.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.41,1:13:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Đây là số phận của chúng ta, Ethan.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.34,1:13:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Chẳng còn cách nào khác đâu.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.17,1:13:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Khoan đã
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.64,1:13:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Anh nói gì cơ?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:44.21,1:13:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Đừng!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.00,1:13:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Làm ơn, đừng!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.40,1:13:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Bắn anh đi!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.05,1:13:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Anh thật sự xin lỗi
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.49,1:13:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Đừng.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:57.59,1:13:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Mất nguồn, đang tắt.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.59,1:14:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Anh đang...\NAnh đang làm gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.03,1:14:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Thế quái nào lại có\N giọng anh trong thứ đó?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.30,1:14:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Anh nói em.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.84,1:14:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Tại sao lại giấu anh chuyện này?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.97,1:14:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Tại sao lại giấu anh chuyện này hả?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.44,1:14:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thế sao anh lại có súng hả?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.05,1:14:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Đó là sự bảo vệ.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:21.08,1:14:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Khỏi cái gì?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.42,1:14:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Anh vừa nói là.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.62,1:14:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Nơi này, nó... nó chỉ toàn bụi với xương.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.05,1:14:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Bảo vệ khỏi gì hả, em?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:28.06,1:14:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Anh có định bắt chết em không hả,\Nanh trai?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.53,1:14:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Gì cơ?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.47,1:14:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Em đang mất trí rồi đấy.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:44.20,1:14:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Trong cái thứ đó không bao giờ là anh cả.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:50.08,1:14:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Jude, đưa em khẩu súng đi.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.08,1:14:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Mình đang kiểm soát.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.74,1:14:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sao em lại lừa anh?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.15,1:14:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Làm ơn đấy.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.60,1:15:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Làm ơn đi, Jude.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:00.55,1:15:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- Đưa em khẩu súng.\N- Ở yên đó.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:02.89,1:15:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- Chỉ...\N- Ở yên tại đó.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.09,1:15:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Chỉ việc đưa em khẩu súng thôi, Jude.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.26,1:15:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Xin anh đấy.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.54,1:15:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Anh biết bộ xương em\N ở đó như thế nào rồi, phải chứ?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.35,1:15:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Cảnh báo...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:28.60,1:15:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Vụ nổ hạt nhân sẽ xảy ra trong hai giờ nữa.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:37.02,1:15:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Làm ơn.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.00,1:15:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Đi!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:01.25,1:16:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Anh muốn nói em anh định làm gì?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.38,1:16:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Saving you from yourself. Move.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.27,1:16:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[ELECTRICITY POPtín hiệu]
Dialogue: 0,1:16:25.57,1:16:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like we found our problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.31,1:16:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,GRID: Emergency reroute\Nrequired.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.52,1:16:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,ETHAN: It's so fried.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:40.05,1:16:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got to reroute the power.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:44.02,1:16:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Archie, reroute stability.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:46.76,1:16:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,ARCHIE: Reroute stability 30%,\NEthan.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.63,1:16:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Hit it.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:51.43,1:16:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:53.10,1:16:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[POWERING UP]
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.07,1:16:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[POWERING DOWN]
Dialogue: 0,1:16:57.34,1:16:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,ARCHIE: Power reroute failure.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:58.67,1:17:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it.\NGive us a fucking chance.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.21,1:17:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[RUMBLING]
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.35,1:17:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,GRID: Evacuate service chamber.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:08.48,1:17:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Eth, look out! The door.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.49,1:17:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[GRUNTS]
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.49,1:17:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,GRID: Depressurization required.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.36,1:17:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Grid, override.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:17.62,1:17:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,GRID: Unable to comply.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.13,1:17:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,ETHAN: It won't work.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.43,1:17:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to manually pull\Nthe backup breaker
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.23,1:17:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,while the room\Nis depressurized.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.30,1:17:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I going to die in here?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.54,1:17:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,GRID: Purging O2.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:33.11,1:17:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You aren't.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.41,1:17:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,JUDE: Ethan!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.58,1:17:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ethan!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.19,1:17:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.18,1:18:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,YOUNG ETHAN: Stars?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:54.86,1:18:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[DISTORTED]\NHow are we like stars?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.17,1:19:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[AIR RUSHING]
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.34,1:19:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,GRID: Power restored.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.74,1:19:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Nuclear core active.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.25,1:20:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,JUDE: Grid, system status.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.89,1:20:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,GRID: Chronicle systems online.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.69,1:20:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Critical systems nominal.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.59,1:20:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,37 phút to portal launch.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.69,1:20:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank fucking Christ.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.93,1:20:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[LAUGHS]
Dialogue: 0,1:20:17.24,1:20:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Where does this go?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:26.38,1:20:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[PANEL BEEPS]
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.38,1:21:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.89,1:21:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No. No.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:39.99,1:21:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- What?\N- How didn't I-I see it?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:42.92,1:21:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,See what?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.56,1:21:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,ETHAN: The... The...\NThe... The future. It's...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:46.06,1:21:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already written.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.53,1:21:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We're just turning\Nthe fucking pages.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.40,1:21:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,JUDE: Give that to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.04,1:21:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:55.94,1:21:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ethan, stop playing games.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.91,1:22:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I am going to die.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.98,1:22:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What happens next, Jude?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.05,1:22:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I thought that\Nwhen we changed my death,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:10.89,1:22:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,it meant that I could\Nchange fate...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.82,1:22:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,mine, Xanthe's, everyone's.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:16.39,1:22:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But the skeleton, it...\Nit's still there.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.63,1:22:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,My skeleton is still here.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:20.33,1:22:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are we still talking about\Na fucking skeleton?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:22.70,1:22:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,ETHAN: My skeleton is still here
Dialogue: 0,1:22:24.50,1:22:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,because\Nwe can't change anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.37,1:22:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything was always\Ngoing to play out this way.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:29.94,1:22:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what we do,\Nit's leading us to that moment.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:34.74,1:22:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're confusing yourself,\NEthan.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.68,1:22:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:37.88,1:22:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to go home,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:39.71,1:22:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're going to shoot me\Nin the head,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.41,1:22:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm going to rot\Nin that hallway for 400 years.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:47.52,1:22:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I not useful to you anymore,\Nbrother?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.46,1:22:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't lie to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:56.10,1:22:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would I? Why would I?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.43,1:23:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you know I'm never\Ngoing to see her again.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:02.70,1:23:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm protecting you.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.07,1:23:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,By putting a fucking gun\Nto my head?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:06.57,1:23:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[CRYING]
Dialogue: 0,1:23:09.74,1:23:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- Archie...\N- Put that fucking thing away.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.44,1:23:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- ARCHIE: Yes, Ethan?\N- ...play last recording.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:13.38,1:23:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[INDISTINCT SHOUTING]
Dialogue: 0,1:23:19.72,1:23:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,ETHAN: Please, no. No.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:20.96,1:23:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.42,1:23:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Find me!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.89,1:23:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.93,1:23:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- I wouldn't.\N- ETHAN: No!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:29.73,1:23:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[GUNSHOT]
Dialogue: 0,1:23:33.63,1:23:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuck.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:35.77,1:23:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The second I got here, it was...\Nit was staring me in the face.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:39.01,1:23:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I just didn't want\Nto believe it was you.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.74,1:23:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's not me, Ethan.\N- ETHAN: Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.81,1:23:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Why wait until we get back\Nto do it?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:45.15,1:23:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not just fucking do it now?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.51,1:23:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you do that to me?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:48.75,1:23:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not the plan.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:49.98,1:23:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What plan?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.69,1:23:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- We've got to get out of here.\N- What fucking plan?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:53.19,1:23:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If we leave now,\Nwe can change everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.76,1:23:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Get off. Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.76,1:23:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- What fucking plan?\N- You've got to trust me.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:59.83,1:24:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm protecting you,\NGod damn it.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.63,1:24:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:03.43,1:24:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuck.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.73,1:24:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,GRID: 30 phút\Nto portal launch.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:10.54,1:24:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in control.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.67,1:24:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in control.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.94,1:24:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is alive, Ethan.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:15.18,1:24:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no reason\Nwe can't live here.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.01,1:24:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And leave everyone to die?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:21.45,1:24:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,JUDE: Ethan.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.05,1:24:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no masks.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:28.19,1:24:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't stop them.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:31.13,1:24:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I saved you, Ethan,\Nbut we can't save everyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.60,1:24:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You've lost your fucking mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.87,1:24:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay away from me.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.81,1:24:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,JUDE: Ethan!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:51.68,1:24:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,My birthday.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:57.58,1:25:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I've made a terrible mistake.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.82,1:25:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't play God.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.23,1:25:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't belong\Nin God's playground.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.13,1:25:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Jude, what the fuck?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.70,1:25:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going to find\Nwhat you're looking for.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.80,1:25:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ethan, no!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.68,1:25:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ethan!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.28,1:25:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no other way.\NEthan!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:25.78,1:25:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,RICHARD: We don't belong\Nin God's playground.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:28.02,1:25:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't belong\Nin God's playground.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:30.28,1:25:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't belong\Nin God's playground.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.05,1:25:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,JUDE: It won't change anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.82,1:25:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,RICHARD: Maybe one day\NI'll be there, and I can say...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.72,1:25:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,say this to your face.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.80,1:25:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,All of this was for you, Ethan.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:47.84,1:25:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If I could give you the life\NI never had,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.74,1:25:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,then you'd know\Nthat I love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.01,1:25:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:03.85,1:26:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the hardest thing,\Nto admit what you're afraid of.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:09.76,1:26:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I never had a father.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.99,1:26:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if you know that.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:19.10,1:26:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do I run away?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.07,1:26:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have been there\Nfor you.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:26.81,1:26:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have been there\Nfor you.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:30.91,1:26:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know how.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:35.28,1:26:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:38.15,1:26:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:45.86,1:26:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuck.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.73,1:26:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Grid, dial home.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:50.33,1:26:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[BEEtín hiệu]
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.70,1:26:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,SELENE: Richard, where are you?\NWhat have you done to him?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:57.10,1:26:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweetheart, I don't have time\Nto explain.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:59.31,1:27:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I need you to take Ethan\Nand leave the house.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.01,1:27:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Meet me where we first met.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:03.38,1:27:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,SELENE: No. What? No.\NI don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:05.31,1:27:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to have\Nto tell him yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:07.98,1:27:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ethy.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:09.92,1:27:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ethy, I need you to go\Nfor a little walk with your mom.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.79,1:27:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,YOUNG ETHAN: Papa,\NI want to stay here.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:15.39,1:27:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,RICHARD: I will meet you.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:17.12,1:27:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:19.29,1:27:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to trust me now.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:23.16,1:27:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,GRID: Entry granted.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:25.03,1:27:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,RICHARD: End call.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:38.15,1:27:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Jude.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:41.95,1:27:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,JUDE: I can't let you do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:43.75,1:27:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,REGINA: What are you thinking\Nnow, Richard?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:46.42,1:27:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,RICHARD: This isn't about\Nfinding a cure anymore, is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:50.09,1:27:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to escape,\Njust leave the world behind.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:55.00,1:27:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no cure.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:57.76,1:27:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That message was sent\Nby someone.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:59.40,1:28:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There must be a cure.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.24,1:28:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:02.87,1:28:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too late for that.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:05.04,1:28:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This world is done, Richard.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:10.28,1:28:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to save them all?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:12.28,1:28:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Most of them would\Ncut your throat
Dialogue: 0,1:28:13.45,1:28:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,for one breath of fresh air.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.28,1:28:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,They wouldn't know what to do\Nwith another chance.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:19.99,1:28:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:21.42,1:28:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we could save them,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:23.79,1:28:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,humans are a virus.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.06,1:28:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The Earth will heal but never\Nwhile we're suffocating it.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:28.40,1:28:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- This isn't the way.\N- This is the only way.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:33.30,1:28:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The Earth needs time\Nwithout us, so we jump ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:37.04,1:28:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Start again, or humanity\Ndies for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:40.17,1:28:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Who, your chosen few?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:46.18,1:28:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you've lost people,\Nbut you can't...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:48.05,1:28:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't about me, Richard.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:54.05,1:28:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:56.32,1:28:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,People are going to have to die.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:00.93,1:29:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not an easy decision,\Nbut it's the right one.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.90,1:29:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not what we want.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:06.10,1:29:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's what we need.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:09.80,1:29:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to have faith.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:12.94,1:29:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the scientist here.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:15.08,1:29:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to talk about faith?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:18.21,1:29:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not risking the survival\Nof humanity on your faith.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:22.35,1:29:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,BILLY: Hey, Richard.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:23.95,1:29:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Just wanted to say\Nthank you so much
Dialogue: 0,1:29:25.22,1:29:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,for giving me this chance.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:26.89,1:29:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I've run the numbers,\Nand I'm sure it will work.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:28.92,1:29:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got the design team working\Non a rough outline as we speak.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:32.86,1:29:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,An outline for what?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:35.46,1:29:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:38.50,1:29:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.\NDid Richard not authorize this?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:41.20,1:29:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it going to work or not?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.94,1:29:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:46.84,1:29:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I mean,\Nit will take some time,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.34,1:29:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,but I think we can eventually\Njerry rig the Chronicle
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.98,1:29:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,to fire a person one way,\Nkind of like a...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:54.42,1:29:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,a slingshot or a...\Nor a catapult.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:57.99,1:30:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's suicide.\NYou're going to kill someone.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:00.32,1:30:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,With some kind of protective\Nsuit, they might have a chance.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.56,1:30:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,All we need is one person\Nto fix the power
Dialogue: 0,1:30:04.26,1:30:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,on the Chronicle\Nin the future, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.46,1:30:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We fix the power,\Nshe opens up the portal,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.46,1:30:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and we can go safely through.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:11.17,1:30:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,REGINA: The tín hiệu came back.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:12.90,1:30:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There's oxygen there.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:14.24,1:30:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It proves the plan\Nhas already worked.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:16.54,1:30:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Earth regrows only because\Nmankind doesn't make it.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.54,1:30:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,RICHARD: No!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:25.01,1:30:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe\Nit's the only way.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:29.58,1:30:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I've locked the system\Nso only Ethan's DNA
Dialogue: 0,1:30:33.02,1:30:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,can activate the Chronicle\Nat the other end.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:35.96,1:30:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody sent for him,\Nand whether you believe or not,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:40.23,1:30:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,you need him if you want\Nto open the portal.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:46.30,1:30:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you do it?\NCan you get one person through?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:49.37,1:30:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I think it might\Nbe possible,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:50.87,1:30:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's Richard's science,\Nso...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:52.44,1:30:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you make it work?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:55.31,1:30:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- Can you make it work?\N- Yes!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.05,1:31:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[RICHARD'S BODY THUDS]
Dialogue: 0,1:31:05.95,1:31:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[CRYING]
Dialogue: 0,1:31:07.49,1:31:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, fuck! Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:10.36,1:31:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[SHOUTS]
Dialogue: 0,1:31:13.43,1:31:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:15.20,1:31:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:16.53,1:31:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it, stop! Stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:19.93,1:31:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Jackson, I-I don't...\NI don't...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.30,1:31:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Go down with a team.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:25.17,1:31:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure the boy stays alive.\NYou will be his guardian.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:29.18,1:31:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Let nothing happen to him.\NYou understand?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:32.55,1:31:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the key to everything now.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:36.12,1:31:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:08.32,1:32:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,GRID: 30 phút\Nto portal launch.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:11.05,1:32:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuck you.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:13.32,1:32:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You fucking liar!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.52,1:32:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,All this time, you used me!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:18.63,1:32:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You used me.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:20.59,1:32:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,They used us.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.56,1:32:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just a kid, man.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:30.17,1:32:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,They're still coming, Ethan,\Neven if you try and stop them,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:33.54,1:32:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and the world you care\Nso much about,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:36.11,1:32:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,they died for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:38.55,1:32:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That can't be true.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:40.31,1:32:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't change the past.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.98,1:32:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we could,\Nwhat would happen to this place?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:48.96,1:32:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What would happen to us?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:50.62,1:32:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.96,1:32:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But we can't leave\Nmillions of people to die!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:55.26,1:32:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,They have already died!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:58.23,1:33:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already happened, man!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:01.60,1:33:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no cure!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:06.64,1:33:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Eth, you said it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:09.74,1:33:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Things can't be changed,\Nlittle brother.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:16.28,1:33:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not your brother.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:23.56,1:33:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You sound like your father now.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.33,1:33:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, if he had listened\Nto Jackson, he'd still be here.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:33.07,1:33:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Only the strong survive, Ethan.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:41.78,1:33:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So you bought yourself a place\Nin the new world.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.21,1:33:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you have to sacrifice?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:51.08,1:33:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:53.62,1:33:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Xanthe?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:01.66,1:34:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I am your family.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:05.13,1:34:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I did this for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:09.04,1:34:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You did this for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.51,1:34:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,There has to be another way.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:18.55,1:34:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to stop this thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:21.35,1:34:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- No, I can't let you.\N- I have to stop this thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:26.75,1:34:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no other way.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:28.76,1:34:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[GRUNTS]
Dialogue: 0,1:34:29.82,1:34:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our fate.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:31.39,1:34:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- [ETHAN GRUNTS]\N- There is no other way.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:34.06,1:34:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[GRUNTS]
Dialogue: 0,1:34:39.30,1:34:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- What did you say?\N- I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:41.17,1:34:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- No, no, no!\N- I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:42.50,1:34:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:44.37,1:34:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- Fight me.\N- [CHOKING]
Dialogue: 0,1:34:46.27,1:34:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ethan, Ethan, Ethan.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:47.84,1:34:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight me.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:49.41,1:34:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- Fight me.\N- Please!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:51.51,1:34:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- No! No!\N- Fight me!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:53.25,1:34:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:59.35,1:35:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:01.26,1:35:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do it!\NDon't do it!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:03.22,1:35:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- Fight me! Fight me!\N- Please, no, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:06.39,1:35:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight me!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:07.39,1:35:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:09.53,1:35:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You got to fight\Nfor yourself now.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:11.83,1:35:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight me!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:14.37,1:35:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Help.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:16.60,1:35:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[SCREAMS]
Dialogue: 0,1:35:19.37,1:35:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:20.64,1:35:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You got to fight me.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:23.61,1:35:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.45,1:35:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:36.72,1:35:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It is me.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:41.16,1:35:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I can change.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:46.77,1:35:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:51.14,1:35:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[GUNSHOT]
Dialogue: 0,1:35:59.65,1:36:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[BREATHING SHAKILY]
Dialogue: 0,1:36:05.79,1:36:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[CRYING]
Dialogue: 0,1:36:13.33,1:36:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ohh, geez.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:44.69,1:36:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[DEVICE BEEtín hiệu]
Dialogue: 0,1:37:31.34,1:37:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[COMPUTER BEEtín hiệu]
Dialogue: 0,1:37:42.65,1:37:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Distinguished friends,\Nyou have stood with me
Dialogue: 0,1:37:46.32,1:37:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,while you watched your world\Nfall down around you.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:50.32,1:37:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our time.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:53.63,1:37:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Each one of you\Nhas played a part
Dialogue: 0,1:37:55.33,1:37:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,in bringing us to this point.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:57.93,1:38:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,History will not forget you.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:01.33,1:38:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This day will be marked\Nas the day that we proved
Dialogue: 0,1:38:04.54,1:38:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,that we will not go quietly\Ninto the night,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:08.51,1:38:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,the day the human race\Ntook control of its fate.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:20.02,1:38:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I have it on good authority\Nthat you are going to grow up
Dialogue: 0,1:38:22.96,1:38:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,to be someone very important.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:26.73,1:38:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This is going to hurt,\Nbut it will help you become
Dialogue: 0,1:38:30.00,1:38:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,who you are meant to be.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:32.87,1:38:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,One day you'll understand it.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:36.40,1:38:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You will want to trust what you\Ncan see with your own eyes,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:39.34,1:38:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,but it won't be enough,\Nand you'll need to make a choice
Dialogue: 0,1:38:43.31,1:38:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,about whether you believe\Nin something bigger.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:47.81,1:38:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- Archie?\N- ARCHIE: Yes, Ethan?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:57.06,1:38:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone is here.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:58.99,1:39:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,ARCHIE: Who is here, Ethan?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:08.44,1:39:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:12.97,1:39:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[BREATHES DEEPLY]
Dialogue: 0,1:39:21.78,1:39:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:38.90,1:39:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,YOUNG ETHAN: Believe in...\Nbelieve in what?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:45.44,1:39:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Believe in people.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:50.04,1:39:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- No!\N- Fight me!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:53.58,1:39:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,RICHARD: I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:24.68,1:40:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,GRID: Incoming particle stream.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:31.19,1:40:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ethan.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:36.79,1:40:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a liability.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:39.06,1:40:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot him.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:40.63,1:40:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave him here.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:42.00,1:40:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we're gone,\Nit won't matter.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:44.20,1:40:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember the drill.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:46.50,1:40:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We have one shot.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:48.54,1:40:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Once the portal opens, we have\N30 seconds to clear through.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:53.67,1:40:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,GRID: 10, 9, 8, 7, 6,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:58.95,1:41:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,5, 4, 3, 2, 1, 0.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:11.83,1:41:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Tether interrupted.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:14.56,1:41:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Shutting down.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:25.67,1:41:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:27.77,1:41:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:31.48,1:41:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No. No.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:33.71,1:41:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:36.02,1:41:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:57.20,1:41:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[RATTLING]
Dialogue: 0,1:42:13.02,1:42:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,ChroniCorp's headquarters\Nwere raided just moments ago
Dialogue: 0,1:42:16.62,1:42:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,after this news station\Nreceived an anonymous broadcast.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:20.73,1:42:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Officials seized hundreds\Nof believed-extinct plants.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:24.90,1:42:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If what we are hearing is true,\Nthis may be the second chance
Dialogue: 0,1:42:27.63,1:42:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,the world so desperately needs\Nfor ecological regeneration.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:31.94,1:42:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Religious groups are already\Ncalling it the deus ex machina,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:35.18,1:42:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,or God out of the machine.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:40.65,1:42:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,GRID: Entry request.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:43.82,1:42:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Entry request.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:48.86,1:42:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Security override.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:50.79,1:42:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOOR OPENS]
Dialogue: 0,1:43:00.97,1:43:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Xanthe Whyte?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:18.02,1:43:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[GASPS]
Dialogue: 0,1:43:25.99,1:43:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[CRYING]
Dialogue: 0,1:44:39.20,1:44:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,YOUNG ETHAN: Stars?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:41.07,1:44:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,How are we like stars?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:44.11,1:44:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Silly.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:46.81,1:44:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Here.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:48.74,1:44:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, try this.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:53.15,1:44:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What's between us?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:55.32,1:44:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Your hands.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:56.32,1:44:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:57.42,1:45:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:01.19,1:45:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Imagine for a moment that we are\Nall physically connected
Dialogue: 0,1:45:04.99,1:45:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,by the very fabric\Nof the universe.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:10.70,1:45:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,An invisible field\Nthat bonds us together,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:14.27,1:45:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,everything in the universe.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:16.97,1:45:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's you, me, the stars.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:25.21,1:45:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We are all connected\Nthrough time.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:31.25,1:45:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see, Ethy,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:32.85,1:45:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,even when I'm not with you,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:36.02,1:45:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,we are always together.
